----------------
ENTITY SPAWNING:
----------------
Steps:
1. Create an entity object
2. Create entity body
3. (Optional) Set entity position
4. Add entity to GameMap

Code:                           |   Or:
val newEntity = ZombieRunner()  |   GameMap.spawn(ZombieRunner().apply { createBody(); setPosition(mapCoords) })
newEntity.createBody()          |
newEntity.setPosition(5f, 5f)   |
GameMap.spawn(newEntity)        |

Expected behaviour:
New entity will be spawned into the world.

------------------
ENTITY DESPAWNING:
------------------
Steps:
1. Despawn entity

Code:
entity.despawn()

Expected behaviour:
Entity will be despawned on the next world tick.
